caption:
It’s Backyard Asada Season! ☀️

This season marks a time for gathering outdoors and celebrating community and culture around the grill. Just last week, we gathered for our third annual Backyard Asada Celebration right here in Austin, TX! Our Siete Culinary Team cooked up a delicious meal alongside our talented chef friends from @veracruztacos, @ensenadatx, @livismexicue, and @tareaustin. 🧑‍🍳

We enjoyed a variety of tasty dishes, live music by @mariachicorazondetejas and @moneychicha, a DJ set by @djzetroc, crafts for kiddos by @thinkeryatx, flowers courtesy of @petalsonpedals.atx, a photo booth by @homesteadphotoboothco, mini prints by @lucky_shot_mini_prints + art by @vivalapainter & @artmandosilva, and exclusive paleta flavors from @lovemomandpops! It was a blast to share this tradition with our Austin community for another year—thanks for coming out and showing your support! Juntos es Mejor. ❤️

P.S. We’re bringing a Backyard Asada celebration to SoCal on May 29th, too! Tickets available at the link in our bio, limited space available! 🎟️
